The Halal Guys is fast casual restaurant that serves sandwiches and platters with chicken, beef gyro, and/or falafel and white and/or hot sauce. You have the option to add sides including hummus, baba ganouj, falafel, or fries to your order. For drinks, they have Coca Cola beverages and bottled beverages.  I ordered the combo platter. This platter consisted of orange colored rice, chicken and gyro meat, lettuce, tomato, kalamata olives, and their signature white sauce. I felt that it could have had more white sauce than what was provided. It was glad that my friend requested white sauce on the side so they came in packets and was able to add more to my platter. I was on the fence to add hummus but I'm glad I did. For signing up for the rewards program, I got a complimentary fountain soda and side. The wavy fries were crispy and tasted fresh.
A good place to family friendly environment, the only con for this place is more desserts options.
